main event: An unidentified flying object was sighted in Natrona, Pennsylvania on August 29, 1968.
interesting points: The object was observed for 15 minutes,The observer reported the object moving slowly across the sky,The object was described as a bright, round shape with no visible means of propulsion,The object made no noise during the sighting,The sighting concluded with insufficient data for evaluation.
witness description: the observer, who completed a form on the sighting
